  displayTitle: Bounce By Moonlight
  theme: 1
  openingStory: Dessert is safe, but a moonbeam has revealed a hidden road of enormous
    springy leaves. Gassy Gorilla volunteers before anyone can define careful.
  successStory: Three moon-leaf launches later, the old ruins are awake and Gassy
    Gorilla has discovered a dignified new way to be flung.
  lessonText: Land on the broad glowing leaves for a free launch. No fart fuel required.
  failureHintText: Aim for the broad center leaf. The bounce triggers automatically
    on contact.
